yhow for - when my sisters turned to work, my young sister up to Smith, my eldest sister lives there had to pay her out of her wages. So instead of she getting twelve shilling a week, she got ten and six. She had to pay the young sister eighteenpence to w
ork there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5537491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3081566\charrsid3634336 She didn't have any wages, the young sister?
