Yes. So - that was all but it wasn't very often I was late. Then I come back in the dinner hour and go out with the - errands. Same in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5537491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3081566\charrsid3634336 You've told me the hours that you worked?
