urday nights. Ten o'clock was our time, but - then you were out delivering until - after ten o'clock, and then - time you come back and bring in all your - farming stuff it was eleven o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5537491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3081566\charrsid3634336 So that was a long day?
