Working with - Rodda, butcher. But not learning the trade. Just an errand boy I started as.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5537491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3081566\charrsid3634336 What hours did you work there?
