Well I had various hours because - Mondays - and Wednesdays - was killing days. 
Well I had to be out to - Taldis, that's where the slaughterhouse was, five o'clock for killing days. That's the - Mondays and - Wednesdays, and the other days - it was - about half past six when I used to have to go out there and do some milking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5537491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3081566\charrsid3634336 So you did milking before you started at the shop?
