Would your sisters - would she have been able to unbend with them more do you think or was it the same with all of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10821394 TT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3081566\charrsid3634336 Oh I think it was same with all of us.
