\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3542215\charrsid3634336 carol}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3081566\charrsid3634336  singers in the streets?
